                <mxCell id="s4_desc" value="Non-blocking I/O. Thread &lt;b&gt;yields&lt;/b&gt; during wait, does other work, handles result via &lt;b&gt;callback/await&lt;/b&gt;." style="text;html=1;fontSize=11;fontColor=#868e96;align=left;" parent="1" vertex="1">
